{"tid":861153,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講廣東話入 數字術語","createTime":"2018-10-14T01:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T02:47:02.000Z","uid":58218,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41697c7066f54db973625feac07aec1d7dd9f4b3","tid":861153,"uid":58218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n今日係酒樓飲茶 枱號222 <br />\n呀姐俾野食個陣問左句 「依度係咪三條二」<br />\n令我係度諗 <br />\n到底三十 四十 或者連續相同數字 （111,222,3333)<br />\n有冇得用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一隻</span></span></span>中文字去代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n例如我會講 <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">孖</span></span>八 <span style=\"color: pink;\">廿</span>一  但三十以上我就唔識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c62462a6b8cf0c0e11ea7ceef5f814d95414a6","tid":861153,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"孨二囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11647571a20efde1e958bb1b67e81ff892deb17","tid":861153,"uid":58218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30c62462a6b8cf0c0e11ea7ceef5f814d95414a6","tid":861153,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"孨二囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"想問下點讀"},{"pid":"c851ca7007f61bee9eeb9dd03f55bffa30d5d909","tid":861153,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:35:32.000Z","msg":"卅二=三十二"},{"pid":"87bc42631a55871b36b7c0b7aa3c44e5ecc951a5","tid":861153,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:43:37.000Z","msg":"廿=20<br />\n卅=30<br />\n卌=40<br />\n皕=200"},{"pid":"abaf4ffe17820606c38daf68645aaba8d012b9f7","tid":861153,"uid":125976,